SELECT
  i_brand_id AS brand_id,
  i_brand AS brand,
  SUM(ss_ext_sales_price) AS ext_price
FROM filtered_dates, store_sales, item
WHERE
  d_date_sk = ss_sold_date_sk AND ss_item_sk = i_item_sk AND i_manager_id = 100
GROUP BY
  i_brand,
  i_brand_id
ORDER BY
  ext_price DESC,
  i_brand_id
LIMIT 100

SELECT

  AND ss_item_sk = i_item_sk
  AND i_manager_id = 100

GROUP BY

SELECT
  i_brand_id AS brand_id,
  i_brand AS brand,
  SUM(ss_ext_sales_price) AS ext_price
FROM (
  SELECT
    *
  FROM date_dim
  WHERE
    d_moy = 12 AND d_year = 2000
) AS date_dim, store_sales, (
  SELECT
    *
  FROM item
  WHERE
    i_manager_id = 100
) AS item
WHERE
  d_date_sk = ss_sold_date_sk AND ss_item_sk = i_item_sk
GROUP BY
  i_brand,
  i_brand_id
ORDER BY
  ext_price DESC,
  i_brand_id
LIMIT 100

WITH sales_aggregate AS (
    SELECT i_brand_id, i_brand, SUM(ss_ext_sales_price) AS ext_price
    FROM date_dim, store_sales, item
    WHERE d_date_sk = ss_sold_date_sk
        AND ss_item_sk = i_item_sk
        AND i_manager_id = 100
        AND d_moy = 12
        AND d_year = 2000
    GROUP BY i_brand_id, i_brand
)
SELECT i_brand_id AS brand_id, i_brand AS brand, ext_price
FROM sales_aggregate
ORDER BY ext_price DESC, i_brand_id
LIMIT 100

  SUM(ss_ext_sales_price) AS ext_price
FROM store_sales

GROUP BY

LIMIT 100
